---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fajar Maftuh Fadli">
  <Section>
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-black text-slate-50">Fajar Maftuh Fadli</h1>
    <p class="pb-6">
      DevOps Engineer · Cloud Architect · Infrastructure Automation
    </p>
    <p>
      I design, automate, and secure cloud infrastructure that scales — from
      startups to enterprise systems. Specializing in GCP, Terraform,
      monitoring, and reliability engineering.
    </p>
    <ul class="flex list-none! space-x-4">
      <li><a href="/projects">View Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="/cv">Download CV</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact Me</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      I'm a DevOps Engineer focused on building reliable, secure, and scalable
      cloud systems. My work lives at the interSection of infrastructure
      automation, observability, and system design. I specialize in Google Cloud
      Platform, infrastructure-as-code, and enterprise-scale environments —
      helping organizations move from fragile setups to structured, automated,
      and resilient architectures.
    </p>
    <p>I care about:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc">
      <li>Clean system design</li>
      <li>Least-privilege security</li>
      <li>Cost efficiency</li>
      <li>Reliability over hype</li>
      <li>Automation over manual ops</li>
      <li>Simplicity over complexity</li>
    </ul>
    <q>If it can be automated, it should be automated.</q>
  </Section>
</Layout>
